[SN]TITLE[SN]
Petrol bomb thrown through window of house in Ballykeel estate, Ballymena

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A petrol bomb has been thrown through the window of a house in Ballymena.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
It was thrown through the front window of the house at Barra Drive in the town's Ballykeel estate at about 03:45 BST on Saturday.
The petrol bomb set fire to window blinds and a chair and caused extensive smoke damage to the living room.
No-one was in the house at the time of the attack. Police have appealed for anyone with information to contact them.
